HEADWORD: Imprecatory
<hw>Im"pre*ca*to*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of the nature
of, or containing, imprecation; invoking evil; <as>as, the
<ex>imprecatory</ex> psalms</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Imprecision</ent>⟦br⟧
